entry.title: Tie Dye Patterned Adhesive Vinyl (10 different patterns)
entry.summary:
Vendor: ScriptDesigns
Type: Patterned Adhesive Vinyl
Price: 4.50 - 5.50 (10 variants)

The quality and depth of colour in our prints will amaze you!  Beware of competitors who are trying to immitate us.  Honestly, they can't match up. 

We print professionally on permanent Oracal 651 equivalent vinyl (Orajet)

These sheets have vivid colours and a gloss finish not rendered well by the pictures.

This vinyl is outdoor durable for up to 3 years and may be used on projects just like your regular Oracal or other brands of non-patterned vinyl.  However, due to its printed nature, if it will be exposed to the elements or in contact with water or hands on a regular basis, we highly recommend you add the laminating option.

For more information, please see the Category definition.

Note:  Orders containing patterned products may need 3 to 4 additional working days to process.
